channel.title: Released [VB6] RS Projects
channel.description:
I have released a number of VB6 projects on my web site. These are not your ordinary crappy project source, but some very popular programs that people use. These include:
JAGHaX Auto Fighter 1.0
JAGHaX Auto Typer 2.0
JAGHaX On-Screen Camera 1.0
RS2 Auto Typer 1.0
SCAR Divi Macro 1.1
More will be released like the never before released JAGHaX Ghost Mouse 2.0, with my newly programmed (old now) Ghost Mouse Engine. Another program to look forward to is the Cheat Macro open source project which will be released in probably a month.
I have released the following to help further RS Cheating advancement. However, you must register on my site in order to obtain the source (tracking and security reasons).
Website: http://www.terrankiller.com
Forum: http://www.terrankiller.com/forums/viewforum.php?f=59
Enjoy.
